  "handNote": {
    "lettering": "Simply cut, regular letters of fairly wide module, without serifs. Alpha with broken bar; epsilon with shorter middle stroke; Mu with full length strokes, vertical first and last; omicron almost full size; sigma with horizontal outer strokes, inner strokes almost full width; phi with extended vertical (up to 65mm), small circular eye; omega closed, with tear-drop shape. ",
